.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lilac, brown, mauve
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Color         | aquamarine  | mauve | lilac  | brown |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

