4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
6. the person who likes red is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
