1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the bartender is the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the fan of funk is the owner of the rat##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
