4. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the mechanic is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
