.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, scientist, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, parkour, tennis
1. the engineer is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate   | sprite | almond-milk   | fanta      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 